quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Was there not a period of time when man was nothing to speak of ?"
  76,2,"We created man from a drop of mingled fluid to put him to the test; We gave him hearing and sight;"
  76,3,"We guided him to the right path, whether he was grateful or not."
  76,4,"We have prepared chains, iron collars, and blazing Fire for the disbelievers, but"
  76,5,"the righteous will have a drink mixed with kafur,"